---

---

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
        <h2
            class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-center text-ultimate-blue mb-10 font-heading"
        >
            Frequently Asked Question
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <details
                class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 open:shadow-md"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-4 font-semibold text-ultimate-navy hover:bg-ue-blue-light transition font-heading"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span
                            class="material-icons text-sm text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform"
                            >add</span
                        >
                        IELTS & SAT berguna untuk apa?
                    </div>
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="p-4 text-ultimate-navy/70 text-sm border-t border-ue-blue-light font-body font-light"
                >
                    IELTS dan SAT digunakan sebagai syarat masuk universitas di
                    luar negeri. IELTS mengukur kemampuan bahasa Inggris,
                    sedangkan SAT mengukur kesiapan akademik.
                </div>
            </details>
            <details
                class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-4 font-semibold text-ultimate-navy hover:bg-ue-blue-light transition font-heading"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span
                            class="material-icons text-sm text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform"
                            >add</span
                        >
                        Apa itu IELTS & SAT Placement Test?
                    </div>
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="p-4 text-ultimate-navy/70 text-sm border-t border-ue-blue-light font-body font-light"
                >
                    Test ini dirancang untuk mengukur sejauh mana kemampuan
                    bahasa Inggris dan kemampuan akademik Anda sebelum memulai
                    persiapan tes resmi.
                </div>
            </details>
            <details
                class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-4 font-semibold text-ultimate-navy hover:bg-ue-blue-light transition font-heading"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span
                            class="material-icons text-sm text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform"
                            >add</span
                        >
                        Apa saja yang diujikan dalam IELTS Placement Test?
                    </div>
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="p-4 text-ultimate-navy/70 text-sm border-t border-ue-blue-light font-body font-light"
                >
                    IELTS Placement Test mencakup Listening, Reading, dan
                    Writing dasar untuk memberikan gambaran skor band Anda.
                </div>
            </details>
            <details
                class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-4 font-semibold text-ultimate-navy hover:bg-ue-blue-light transition font-heading"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span
                            class="material-icons text-sm text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform"
                            >add</span
                        >
                        Apa saja yang diujikan dalam SAT Placement Test?
                    </div>
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="p-4 text-ultimate-navy/70 text-sm border-t border-ue-blue-light font-body font-light"
                >
                    SAT Placement Test fokus pada Reading, Writing & Language,
                    serta Math (dengan dan tanpa kalkulator) sesuai format SAT
                    terbaru.
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
